 detail and a commitment to excellence, we create spaces that inspire, elevate, and enrich the lives of those who inhabit them.'=>'S pažnjom posvećenom detaljima i predanošću izvrsnosti, stvaramo prostore koji nadahnjuju, uzdižu i obogaćuju živote onih koji ih nastanjuju.','Title text for the feature areaThe revitalized art gallery is set to redefine cultural landscape.'=>'Revitalizirana umjetnička galerija trebala bi redefinirati kulturni krajolik.','Pattern titleProject details'=>'Pojedinosti projekta','Sample contentExperience the fusion of imagination and expertise with Études Architectural Solutions.'=>'Doživite spoj mašte i stručnosti s Études arhitektonskim rješenjima.','Sample headingArchitectural Solutions'=>'Arhitektonska rješenja','Sample feature headingProject Management'=>'Upravljanje projektom','Sample feature headingConsulting'=>'Savjetovanje','Sample feature headingApp Access'=>'Pristup aplikaciji','Sample feature headingContinuous Support'=>'Trajna podrška','Sample feature contentExperience the fusion of imagination and expertise with Études Architectural Solutions.'=>'Doživite spoj mašte i stručnosti s Études arhitektonskim rješenjima.','Sample feature headingRenovation and restoration'=>'Obnova i restauriranje','Sub-heading of the featuresOur comprehensive suite of professional services caters to a diverse clientele, ranging from homeowners to commercial developers.'=>'Naš sveobuhvatni paket profesionalnih usluga služi raznolikoj klijenteli, od vlasnika kuća do komercijalnih programera.','Heading of the featuresA passion for creating spaces'=>'Strast za stvaranjem prostora','Pattern titleFeature grid, 3 columns'=>'Rešetka značajki, 3 stupca','Question in the FAQ patternCan I apply to be a part of the team or work as a contractor?'=>'Mogu li se prijaviti da budem dio tima ili da radim kao izvođač?','Question in the FAQ patternI\'d like to get to meet fellow architects, how can I do that?'=>'Htio bih upoznati kolege arhitekte, kako to mogu učiniti?','Answer in the FAQ patternÉtudes offers comprehensive consulting, management, design, and research solutions. Our vision is to be at the forefront of architectural innovation, fostering a global community of architects and enthusiasts united by a passion for creating spaces. Every architectural endeavor is an opportunity to shape the future.'=>'Études nudi sveobuhvatna rješenja za savjetovanje, upravljanje, dizajn i istraživanje. Naša je vizija biti na čelu arhitektonskih inovacija, njegujući globalnu zajednicu arhitekata i entuzijasta ujedinjenih strašću za stvaranjem prostora. Svaki arhitektonski pothvat prilika je za oblikovanje budućnosti.','Question in the FAQ patternWhat is your process working in smaller projects?'=>'Kakav je vaš proces rada na manjim projektima?','Heading of the FAQsFAQs'=>'ČPP','Name of the FAQ patternFAQs'=>'ČPP','Pattern titleFAQ'=>'ČPP','<em>Études</em> is not confined to the past—we are passionate about the cutting edge designs shaping our world today.'=>'<em>Études</em> nije ograničen na prošlost — mi smo strastveni prema vrhunskim dizajnima koji oblikuju naš današnji svijet.','Pattern titleCentered statement'=>'Centrirana izjava','I write about finance, management and economy, my book “%1$s” is out now.'=>'Pišem o financijama, menadžmentu i ekonomiji, moja knjiga "%1$s" upravo je izašla.	','Money Studies'=>'Money Studies','Pattern titleCentered statement, small'=>'Centrirana izjava, mala','Sample list itemExclusive access to design insights.'=>'Ekskluzivan pristup uvidima u dizajn.','Sample list itemCase studies that celebrate architecture.'=>'Studije slučaja koje slave arhitekturu.','Sample list itemA world of thought-provoking articles.'=>'Svijet članaka koji potiču na razmišljanje.','Sample headingÉtudes Newsletter'=>'Bilten Études','Windows of a building in Nuremberg, Germany'=>'Prozori zgrade u Nürnbergu, Njemačka','Tourist taking photo of a building'=>'Turist koji fotografira zgradu','Sample list headi